{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Set fixed prices that councils can charge for burials and ban leasehold plots",
        "additional_details": "I would like for the government to create a blanket pricing agreement (fixed fee) in pricing for all local councils. I would like for the government to also remove the leases for all graves. I think plots should only be available to purchase outright (freehold). I think the cost to be buried should not be so high, and that every individual has a right to be buried according to their faith or personal views.",
        "background": "Some councils charge upwards of \u00a34000 to bury one individual. If we consider the cost of living crisis and the levels of poverty in this country, this can place working families at a significant disadvantage and lead to debt.",
